  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong>, then peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> in <strong>half</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>red chilli[es] </strong>in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
