    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely slice your <strong>red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips (as finely as you can!)</p>",
      "order": 3,
