    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>pepper strips</strong> and <strong>sliced onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 7-8 min or until softened</p>",
