    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the vegetables have softened, add your <strong>garam masala</strong>, <strong>ground turmeric</strong> and<strong> tomato paste</strong> to the pan and cook for 1 min</p><p>Add 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[130ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[170ml] </span><strong>cold<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>water</strong> with the juice of the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until the sauce has thickened and begins to coat the vegetables</p><p>Once done, remove the pan from the heat – these are your <strong>curried vegetables</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
