    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut your <strong>paneer</strong> into 6 equal strips per person</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>paneer strips</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 3-4 min, turning once halfway, until golden</p><p>Add your <strong>tortillas</strong> to a plate and pop them in the <strong>microwave</strong> for 20 secs, or until warmed through</p>",
