      "instruction": "<p>Fill the <strong>warmed tortillas</strong> with the<strong> curried vegetables</strong>, <strong>grated carrot</strong>,<strong> golden paneer</strong> and<strong> diced tomato </strong>– these are your<strong> golden paneer Kati rolls</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>spicy coriander chutney</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
